message.body: I also gotta keep myself reined in a bit tonight...but would be down for gathering. My backyard is kind of a weedy swamp so it's not very chill, though we could hang inside my house. If we wanna do a different night (like a Friday or Saturday) where we could all get equally loose I would like that as well!
Let's do a mini hang tonight, like 6-9 (haha). Then find a Fri/Sat to get real loose.
Hey! If you are going to ikea, would you mind grabbing me a pack of the white unscented tea lights...? I can give you some money tonight!
